] \u2013 album cover concept\n{{div col end}}\n\n==Charts==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Weekly charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2014\u201315)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br/>position\n|-\n{{albumchart|Australia|3|artist=Pink Floyd|album=The Endless River|accessdate=15 November 2014|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Austria|1|artist=Pink Floyd|album=The Endless River|accessdate=18 November 2014|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Flanders|1|artist=Pink Floyd|album=The Endless River|accessdate=14 November 2014|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Wallonia|1|artist=Pink Floyd|album=The Endless River|accessdate=14 November 2014|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Brazilian Albums ([[Associa\u00e7\u00e3o Brasileira dos Produtores de Discos|ABPD]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.portalsucesso.com.br/ranking?tipo=10top|title=Ranking ABPD - CD - 24/11/2014 a 30/11/2014|language=Portuguese|publisher=Portal Sucesso|accessdate=12 December 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160604194356/http://www.portalsucesso.com.br/ranking?tipo=10top|archive-date=4 June 2016|url-status=live|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|4\n|-\n{{albumchart|BillboardCanada|1|artist=Pink Floyd|artistid=338856|accessdate=20 November 2014|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Croatia|1|artist=Pink Floyd|album=The Endless River|accessdate=15 November 2014|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Czech|1|artist=Pink Floyd|album=The Endless River|date=201446|accessdate=18 November 2014|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Denmark|1|artist=Pink Floyd|album=The Endless River|rowheader=true|accessdate=17 November 2014}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Netherlands|1|artist=Pink Floyd|album=The Endless River|accessdate=14 November 2014|rowheader=true|}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Finland|4|artist=Pink Floyd|album=The Endless River|rowheader=true|accessdate=16 November 2014}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|France|1|artist=Pink Floyd|album=The Endless Riv