ama (magazine)|Panorama]]|date=12 January 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117050434/http://www.panorama.it/musica/vasco-rossi-innocente-lalbum-venduto-2014/|archive-date=17 November 2015|url-status=live|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n| 2\n|-\n{{albumchart|New Zealand|9|M|title=The Official NZ Music Charts - End of Year Charts 2014| url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141220102708/http://nztop40.co.nz/chart/albums?chart=2614 |rowheader=true}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Polish Albums (ZPAV)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bestsellery.zpav.pl/aktualnosci.php?idaktualnosci=1151|title=Jakie p\u0142yty Polacy kupowali najch\u0119tniej w 2014 roku \u2013 roczne podsumowanie listy OLiS|publisher=[[Polish Society of the Phonographic Industry]]|language=Polish|accessdate=19 January 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150119223817/http://bestsellery.zpav.pl/aktualnosci.php?idaktualnosci=1151|archive-date=19 January 2015|url-status=live|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n| 3\n|-\n{{albumchart|Switzerland|8|M|title=Schweizer Jahreshitparade 2014| url=http://swisscharts.com/charts/jahreshitparade/2014 |rowheader=true}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| UK Albums (OCC)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/the-official-top-40-biggest-selling-artist-albums-of-2014__7579/|title=UK Album Charts|work=Billboard|access-date=21 March 2015|archive-url=https://archive.is/20150224184601/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/the-official-top-40-biggest-selling-artist-albums-of-2014__7579/|archive-date=24 February 2015|url-status=live|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n| 9\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| US ''Billboard'' 200<ref>{{cite magazine|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2014/top-billboard-200-albums|title=Top Billboard 200 Albums: 2014 Year-End Charts|magazine=Billboard|accessdate=2015-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141212203747/http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2014/top-billboard-200-albums|archive-date=12 December 2014|url-status=live|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n| 115\n|-\n!scop